{"tid":901323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慘淪「強姦犯女兒」 曾寶儀曝曾志偉七字回應","createTime":"2018-11-14T02:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T02:10:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e1abe95a61e40331b8f1ccb2886726c96acc6bc8","tid":901323,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T02:10:52.000Z","msg":"港星藍潔瑛3日被發現在家中暴斃多日，享年55歲，震撼演藝圈，過去曾自爆被兩名影壇大哥性侵，曾志偉就被影射是其中一位，引發熱議，曾志偉也親上火線駁斥，並表示不排除提告，女兒曾寶儀年初時也表態相信爸爸，當時回應的影片也再度被起底。<br />\n<br />\n曾志偉疑似性侵藍潔瑛一事，在藍潔瑛去世後又再度被搬上檯面，年初曾寶儀上大陸節目時也曾談過此事，她強調「我絕對嚴厲譴責任何形式的性侵害和性騷擾，但是任何不實的指控和誹謗，也絕不姑息」，也無奈感嘆「在事情還沒查明前，我已經迅速成為『強姦犯女兒』、『全家死光光』&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n對於曾志偉表態「沒有涉入這件事」，曾寶儀也表示絕對相信爸爸，也呼籲外界，「反性侵、反性騷的這個行動，從來不是男生跟女生之間的戰爭，每個人都要關注，不能漠視，畢竟無論是男是女，都有可能成為受害者」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bE4t1LSxpuMPwLdoYN5ZrA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzQ4/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/37692ba1313c016ecd125094628e2698\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FbE4t1LSxpuMPwLdoYN5ZrA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzQ4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F37692ba1313c016ecd125094628e2698&h=10db7df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%85%98%E6%B7%AA-%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%8A%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92-%E6%9B%BE%E5%AF%B6%E5%84%80%E6%9B%9D%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E4%B8%83%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-110000429.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2585%2598%25E6%25B7%25AA-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E7%258A%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25AF%25B6%25E5%2584%2580%25E6%259B%259D%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589-110000429.html&d=ixLiYFCu732OhaqVDeQPpKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=345960dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%85%98%E6%B7%AA-%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%8A%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92-%E6%9B%BE%E5%AF%B6%E5%84%80%E6%9B%9D%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E4%B8%83%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-110000429.html</a>"}]}